My soup and my friends salad were supper tasty and fresh. Service was great, the dishes are a nice size and the Toro Sashimi was super fresh and the texture was excellent. I really enjoyed the place. 
It is a bit hidden inside the Westmount Square Food Court. In case that you would be like me trying to find were is located, I tough was inside one of the towers ans not necessarily inside the food court, where actually is...